====unsupervised learning=====

Unsupervised Machine Learning is a type of Machine ,
Learning where the model learns from data without labels.

-------Types of Unsupervised Learning-------

1. Clustering

Similar data ko groups me divide karta hai.

Example:
Netflix similar users ko group karta hai
Shopping apps similar customers identify karti hain
Algorithms:
K-Means
DBSCAN
Hierarchical Clustering

2. Association

Data me relationships find karta hai.

Example:

“Jo log bread kharidte hain wo butter bhi kharidte hain.”

Algorithm:
Apriori Algorithm

3. Dimensionality Reduction

Large data ko smaller form me convert karta hai.

Example:

100 features ko reduce karke 10 important features banana.

Algorithms:
PCA (Principal Component Analysis)
t-SNE


